==Many languages==
===Interjection===
'''mmm...''', '''mmmmmmm''', '''mmmmmmmmm''' etc., with as many 'm's as necessary to best convey the deliciousness of the upcoming food
# An expression used to show contentment for something, e.g., '''mmm this is a tasty pie'''

===Number===
'''MMM'''
# ([[Roman numerals]]) [[3000]]

